» Welcome to Silverton Reinforcing and Wire Products Pty(Ltd)...


Silverton Reinforcing and Wire Products Pty(Ltd) specialises in the supply, cut and bend of reinforcing steel for the building and civil engineering industries. We also offer the additional service of placing and wiring the product into position.Our product range is complemented by pre-assembled foundation beams, reinforcing mesh, hard drawn wire, brickforce and nails.Our business culture is one of excellent service and delivery of high quality products at very competitive prices. Our well designed rebar yards in Pretoria and Witbank, are capable of handling any size contract. We would like to take this opportunity to introduce you to the variety of our products and services our company has to offer.Please visit our products section, or contact us if you require more information.
















» Our products and services include:






» Supply, cut, bend, deliver, and wire into position of all reinforcing steel

» Pre-assembled foundation beams


» Brickforce


» Reinforcing mesh


» Black tying wire

» Galvanised roof wire


» Round steel nails


» Clout nails


» Panel pins


» Razor wire products




















